          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Final label</h5>
            <p class="card-text"> A free labelling web application to provide pharmacy users a business continuity system or primary labelling system for
               creating patient friendly labels for affixing to prepared medication. Created by using front end technology, (HTML, CSS, JS Jquery) and JSON files . </p>
