          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">RFID lock solution</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              By reverse engineering the electronic RFID locks being used for patient bed side lockers, I was able to create a bespoke RFID programming and database system. This system of programming allows us to have a more robust and reliable system by reducing regular breakdowns and improving patient safety.
This project has allowed me to develop a detailed understanding of passive and active RFID technology.
              </p>

          </div>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <small class="text-muted">RFID Hardware and Software </small>
