          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Pharmacy App Home Page</h5>
            <p class="card-text">With various systems being replaced and the organisation moving to the Microsoft Edge browser, this has provided the pharmacy IT team the opportunity to give our home page a must needed face lift. “Pharmweb” the pharmacy landing page hosts and provide user access to all pharmacy
              applications and tools, mixing the ability to browse, search and use quick links to access commonly used applications. </p>
