          <p class="card-text">With the introduction of a new EHRS system, our old backup labelling system would need to be replaced due to the aging technology
            used to develop it.
As the pharmacy digital manager my role in this project was front heavy with wire framing, researching, design and testing.
The backup label we have released works so well that users can produce a label within 1 minute with no directions, creating a pain free application to be used in the event of a stressful situation.
 </p>
